    "\n",
    "## 6. FEATURE SELECTION\n",
    "\n",
    "In this section, we prepare the data for machine learning by separating features (independent variables) from the target (dependent variable).\n",
    "\n",
    "### Why Feature Selection?\n",
    "- **Features (X):** Input variables used to make predictions\n",
    "- **Target (y):** Output variable we want to predict\n",
    "- This separation is essential for training supervised learning models"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Separate features (X) and target (y)\n",
